ered with insulin, particularly in patients with advanced age and/or renal impairment.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/183446/', '', 'Amitriptyline, Maprotiline, St. John''s Wort, Milnacipran, Levomilnacipran, Doxepin, Duloxetine, Viloxazine, Amoxapine, Imipramine, Esketamine, More', '', 1767369485);
